00:49:01.455 --> 00:49:03.523 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Additional printed copies

00:49:03.523 --> 00:49:06.793 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
may be requested through the congregations.

00:49:06.793 --> 00:49:08.895 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So Monday
—in two days—

00:49:08.895 --> 00:49:11.465 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
you get this one electronically.

00:49:11.465 --> 00:49:14.334 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But now, moving to our next talk.

00:49:14.334 --> 00:49:16.303 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We’re privileged to listen

00:49:16.303 --> 00:49:18.305 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to Brother Anthony Morris,

00:49:18.305 --> 00:49:23.076 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and he’s going to deliver the gripping talk,

00:49:23.076 --> 00:49:26.079 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“This Is It!”

00:49:26.079 --> 00:49:28.415 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I hope that I rendered justice

00:49:28.415 --> 00:49:30.684 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to announcing that title, Brother Morris.

00:49:31.468 --> 00:49:33.470 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I’ll talk to you later on.

00:49:45.282 --> 00:49:48.285 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It ruined my introduction, but that’s all right.

00:49:50.187 --> 00:49:53.256 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But I think all of you would agree

00:49:53.256 --> 00:49:57.294 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
how much we enjoyed the museum video

00:49:57.294 --> 00:49:59.830 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and hearing Brother Fred Franz

00:49:59.830 --> 00:50:03.100 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
—his voice—
talking about after the assassination

00:50:03.100 --> 00:50:07.504 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
of the archduke
that the brothers said, ‘Aha!

00:50:07.504 --> 00:50:10.374 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
‘There it is!
There it is!

00:50:10.374 --> 00:50:13.010 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
What we’ve been waiting for.’

00:50:13.010 --> 00:50:15.412 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Well, that’s very stirring,

00:50:15.412 --> 00:50:17.781 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and then we would have critics saying,

00:50:17.781 --> 00:50:21.118 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
‘Yeah, but you people had other expectations

00:50:21.118 --> 00:50:25.489 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that were not realized,’
and etcetera, you know.

00:50:25.489 --> 00:50:28.959 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But it’s amazing that even the world

00:50:28.959 --> 00:50:33.463 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
recognized that this was unique—1914.

00:50:33.463 --> 00:50:37.067 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
See?
In fact, I’ve had this for many years.

00:50:37.067 --> 00:50:38.435 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I want to show it to you.

00:50:38.435 --> 00:50:41.671 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It’s The New World Magazine.

00:50:41.671 --> 00:50:43.974 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And it was widely read at the time,

00:50:43.974 --> 00:50:48.078 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and I guess about 1931,
they went out of business.

00:50:48.078 --> 00:50:53.083 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But here, 
“End of All Kingdoms in 1914

00:50:53.083 --> 00:50:56.119 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
—‘Millennial Dawners’ 25 Year Prophecy,”

00:50:56.119 --> 00:50:59.356 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
widely read; other newspapers covered it.

00:50:59.356 --> 00:51:01.825 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
They made comments here:

00:51:01.825 --> 00:51:04.494 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“The terrific war outbreak in Europe

00:51:04.494 --> 00:51:07.431 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“has fulfilled an extraordinary prophecy.

00:51:07.431 --> 00:51:10.000 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“For a quarter of a century past,

00:51:10.000 --> 00:51:12.536 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“through preachers and through press,

00:51:12.536 --> 00:51:16.339 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“the ‘International Bible Students,’
best known as ‘Millennial Dawners,’

00:51:16.339 --> 00:51:19.776 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“have been proclaiming
to the world that the Day of Wrath

00:51:19.776 --> 00:51:23.180 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“prophesied in the Bible would dawn in 1914.

00:51:23.180 --> 00:51:25.582 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“‘Look out for 1914!’

00:51:25.582 --> 00:51:30.120 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
has been the cry
of the hundreds of traveling evangelists.”

00:51:30.120 --> 00:51:32.222 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And I appreciate very much how

00:51:32.222 --> 00:51:34.724 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
the Yearbook in 1975

00:51:34.724 --> 00:51:37.360 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
considering our modern-day history

00:51:37.360 --> 00:51:40.163 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
made this beautiful quote:

00:51:40.163 --> 00:51:42.999 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Disappointments about going to heaven

00:51:42.999 --> 00:51:46.403 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“in 1914 really were very minor,

00:51:46.403 --> 00:51:49.706 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“compared with the great expectations realized

00:51:49.706 --> 00:51:51.708 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
in connection with that year.”

00:51:51.708 --> 00:51:53.009 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And it’s amazing.

00:51:53.009 --> 00:51:55.779 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
During the first six months
of 1914, nothing happened.

00:51:55.779 --> 00:51:57.781 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
They were being ridiculed.

00:51:57.781 --> 00:52:01.485 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And then the archduke is assassinated.

00:52:01.485 --> 00:52:04.154 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
This one was particularly released

00:52:04.154 --> 00:52:06.890 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
on August 30, 1914.

00:52:06.890 --> 00:52:11.261 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Millions died in World War I.

00:52:11.261 --> 00:52:14.564 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So it’s Brother Franz’s statement

00:52:14.564 --> 00:52:18.401 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that really gave
the idea for the theme here:

00:52:18.401 --> 00:52:20.971 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“This Is It!”

00:52:20.971 --> 00:52:24.040 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The question arises, Will we have

00:52:24.040 --> 00:52:27.811 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
one or more times
—in the future or even now—

00:52:27.811 --> 00:52:30.780 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
when we can say, “This is it”

00:52:30.780 --> 00:52:34.918 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and have that same exciting fervor

00:52:34.918 --> 00:52:37.821 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
because of Bible prophecy?

00:52:37.821 --> 00:52:39.956 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Well, let’s begin with this one here.

00:52:41.024 --> 00:52:44.161 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Find Daniel chapter 11,

00:52:45.428 --> 00:52:47.464 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Daniel chapter 11.

00:52:51.101 --> 00:52:54.938 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And we’re going to read here verse 40,

00:52:54.938 --> 00:52:57.507 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
or half of it:

00:52:59.376 --> 00:53:02.812 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“In the time of the end the king of the south

00:53:02.812 --> 00:53:07.684 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
(here at Daniel 11:40)
will engage with him in a pushing.”

00:53:08.718 --> 00:53:12.622 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So the Governing Body

00:53:12.622 --> 00:53:17.294 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
has been prayerfully considering recent events.

00:53:17.294 --> 00:53:21.097 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And we know that in 1991,

00:53:21.097 --> 00:53:23.800 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
the Soviet Union came to an end.

00:53:23.800 --> 00:53:28.038 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So who is “the king of the north”?

00:53:29.439 --> 00:53:31.441 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Well, after prayerfully considering it

00:53:31.441 --> 00:53:33.743 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and the matter of the pushing,

00:53:33.743 --> 00:53:38.014 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
we’re assuring you that what we see,

00:53:38.014 --> 00:53:41.952 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
after prayerfully considering it,
is that it’s Russia

00:53:41.952 --> 00:53:44.888 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and its allies
—the king of the north.

00:53:44.888 --> 00:53:46.990 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Now, here’s some reasoning.

00:53:46.990 --> 00:53:50.293 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The Soviet Union disbanded;

00:53:50.293 --> 00:53:52.929 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Russia came up from the rubble

00:53:52.929 --> 00:53:56.666 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
of the Soviet Union, along with its allies.

00:53:56.666 --> 00:54:00.070 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And here are some of the facts.

