00:55:48.812 --> 00:55:52.849 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
notice the very familiar thoughts

00:55:52.849 --> 00:55:56.252 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
from 1 Thessalonians chapter 5,

00:55:56.252 --> 00:55:59.522 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and we’re going to read verse 2

00:55:59.522 --> 00:56:01.524 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and verse 3,

00:56:03.460 --> 00:56:06.996 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
5:2, 3:
“For you yourselves know very well

00:56:06.996 --> 00:56:09.899 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“that Jehovah’s day is coming exactly

00:56:09.899 --> 00:56:12.369 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“as a thief in the night.

00:56:12.369 --> 00:56:15.338 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Whenever it is that they are saying,

00:56:15.338 --> 00:56:18.408 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“‘Peace and security!’

00:56:18.408 --> 00:56:21.444 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
