00:56:29.052 --> 00:56:32.622 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Now, so that we have clear thinking

00:56:32.622 --> 00:56:36.159 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
on the published comments regarding

00:56:36.159 --> 00:56:38.161 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
