that we read, we’ll take you back

00:56:38.161 --> 00:56:41.931 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to the September 15, 2012, Watchtower:

00:56:43.366 --> 00:56:46.703 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“As used here, ‘Jehovah’s day’

00:56:46.703 --> 00:56:50.407 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“refers to the period
that will start with the destruction

00:56:50.407 --> 00:56:52.642 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“of false religion and will culminate

00:56:52.642 --> 00:56:55.578 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“in the war of Armageddon.

00:56:55.578 --> 00:56:59.082 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“However, just before
that day of Jehovah begins,

00:56:59.082 --> 00:57:03.219 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“world leaders will be saying,
‘Peace and security!’

00:57:03.219 --> 00:57:06.556 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
