00:57:55.238 --> 00:57:58.041 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Isn’t that interesting?

00:57:58.041 --> 00:57:59.609 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So keep that in mind.

00:57:59.609 --> 00:58:02.111 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We’ll come back to it,
and that happens

00:58:02.111 --> 00:58:04.514 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to be the case when
the prophecy is fulfilled.

00:58:04.514 --> 00:58:06.850 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Oh, OK.”

00:58:06.850 --> 00:58:08.651 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But, see, we’ll come back

00:58:08.651 --> 00:58:10.987 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to that statement
from The Watchtower shortly.

00:58:10.987 --> 00:58:14.157 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But just consider
(especially those of you here,

00:58:14.157 --> 00:58:16.926 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
many of you are aged,

00:58:16.926 --> 00:58:20.296 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and you’ll remember,

00:58:20.296 --> 00:58:22.432 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
many of you who were
in the truth at the time),

00:58:22.432 --> 00:58:25.535 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
What about the year 1986?

00:58:25.535 --> 00:58:27.737 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The United Nations

00:58:27.737 --> 00:58:30.406 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
