you were like, “OK.”

00:58:49.692 --> 00:58:51.728 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So they were all big.

00:58:51.728 --> 00:58:53.596 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
In fact, the pope at that time

00:58:53.596 --> 00:58:56.432 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
