00:59:07.877 --> 00:59:10.647 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Well, how did
the faithful slave handle all that?

00:59:12.682 --> 00:59:17.654 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So this honors
Jehovah’s faithful slave serving at that time.

00:59:17.654 --> 00:59:20.924 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Here’s what was published
in the ’85 Watchtower,

00:59:20.924 --> 00:59:22.959 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
October 1, page 18.

00:59:22.959 --> 00:59:27.597 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Now, this is some months
before that all started in 1986.

00:59:27.597 --> 00:59:29.999 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Here’s what was stated:

00:59:29.999 --> 00:59:32.936 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Christians cannot say in advance exactly

00:59:32.936 --> 00:59:37.340 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“when the great tribulation will strike.
(Period.)

00:59:37.340 --> 00:59:41.511 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Jehovah has not revealed
‘that day or the hour.’

00:59:41.511 --> 00:59:43.713 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Thus when, for example, the United Nations

00:59:43.713 --> 00:59:46.082 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
