00:59:46.082 --> 00:59:49.018 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“an ‘International Year of Peace,’

00:59:49.018 --> 00:59:51.854 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Christians watch the event with interest.

00:59:51.854 --> 00:59:54.524 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“But they cannot say in advance

00:59:54.524 --> 00:59:58.294 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
