to be the fulfillment of Paul’s words.”

00:59:58.294 --> 01:00:00.496 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Nonetheless, we kept on the watch,

01:00:00.496 --> 01:00:03.299 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
