No.

01:00:16.679 --> 01:00:18.781 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But if you are still there,

01:00:18.781 --> 01:00:22.485 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
go back to 1 Thessalonians chapter 5

01:00:22.485 --> 01:00:25.421 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
—just something to keep in mind here—

01:00:25.421 --> 01:00:29.325 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
sometimes we’ll read
verses 2 and 3 and leave out verse 4.

01:00:31.494 --> 01:00:33.863 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
He writes: “But you, brothers,

01:00:33.863 --> 01:00:37.200 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“you are not in darkness,

01:00:37.200 --> 01:00:40.203 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
so that the day should overtake
you as it would thieves.”

01:00:40.203 --> 01:00:43.006 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So thieves are doing their thievery

01:00:43.006 --> 01:00:46.709 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
