01:00:46.709 --> 01:00:49.412 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So that’s not going to catch us,

01:00:49.412 --> 01:00:52.181 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
the faithful ones worshipping the true God,

01:00:52.181 --> 01:00:56.686 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
obedient to this
earthly part of his organization.

01:00:56.686 --> 01:00:58.988 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So the question comes up—

01:00:58.988 --> 01:01:01.357 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
If you go back to that quote

01:01:01.357 --> 01:01:05.094 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
from the 2004 Watchtower,

01:01:05.094 --> 01:01:08.331 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
‘Prophecies are only fully understood
only after they are fulfilled,’

01:01:08.331 --> 01:01:12.568 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
but we also said, ‘or are in the process

01:01:12.568 --> 01:01:14.871 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
