01:01:14.871 --> 01:01:18.541 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So will

01:01:18.541 --> 01:01:20.677 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
the faithful slave be able to say

01:01:20.677 --> 01:01:23.780 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
in the process of the fulfillment

01:01:23.780 --> 01:01:27.750 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
of this prophecy from 1 Thessalonians:
“This is it!

01:01:29.419 --> 01:01:32.121 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
That’s what we’ve been waiting for”?

01:01:32.121 --> 01:01:34.390 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We’ll have to wait and see.

01:01:37.026 --> 01:01:39.762 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But there’s a word of caution here

01:01:39.762 --> 01:01:43.733 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
we want to pass on to you
because we’re all human.

01:01:43.733 --> 01:01:48.171 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We must keep on the watch,
but please, just don’t be gullible.

01:01:48.171 --> 01:01:51.007 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
You hear a world leader
say something about peace.

01:01:51.007 --> 01:01:54.544 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And then you
start e-mailing or something else

01:01:54.544 --> 01:01:56.979 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
with a social network.

01:01:56.979 --> 01:01:58.981 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“This is it!”

01:02:01.484 --> 01:02:05.154 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Leave the channel to handle such matters.

01:02:05.154 --> 01:02:08.157 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
If the faithful slave is moved by God’s spirit

01:02:08.157 --> 01:02:11.094 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to say that to the brotherhood,

01:02:11.094 --> 01:02:12.995 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and that’s His will, fine.

01:02:12.995 --> 01:02:15.364 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But please don’t be gullible.

01:02:15.364 --> 01:02:19.168 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Stick with the way
Jehovah wants this to operate,

01:02:19.168 --> 01:02:21.938 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and he’ll bless your obedience.

01:02:21.938 --> 01:02:25.174 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Now, you’ll remember
Jehovah’s day begins

01:02:25.174 --> 01:02:28.044 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
as they’re saying,
“Peace and security!”

01:02:28.044 --> 01:02:31.914 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Turn to Revelation chapter 17.

01:02:31.914 --> 01:02:34.350 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
My, what stirring words!

01:02:34.350 --> 01:02:38.755 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
They are familiar,
but it does nourish our figurative hearts

01:02:38.755 --> 01:02:42.125 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
when we read these,

01:02:42.125 --> 01:02:44.927 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
chapter 17,

01:02:44.927 --> 01:02:49.732 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
