01:02:49.732 --> 01:02:52.969 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“He said to me: ‘The waters
that you saw, where the prostitute

01:02:52.969 --> 01:02:55.638 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“‘(the world empire of false religion) is sitting,

01:02:55.638 --> 01:02:58.574 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“‘mean peoples and crowds
and nations and tongues.

01:02:58.574 --> 01:03:01.477 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“‘And the ten horns
that you saw and the wild beast,

01:03:01.477 --> 01:03:03.813 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“‘these will hate the prostitute

01:03:03.813 --> 01:03:06.482 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“‘and will make her devastated and naked,

01:03:06.482 --> 01:03:10.553 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“‘and they will eat up her flesh
and completely burn her with fire.

01:03:10.553 --> 01:03:14.157 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“‘For God put it
into their hearts to carry out his thought,

01:03:14.157 --> 01:03:16.392 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“‘yes, to carry out their one thought

01:03:16.392 --> 01:03:18.628 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“‘by giving their kingdom to the wild beast,

01:03:18.628 --> 01:03:22.431 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
until the words of God
will have been accomplished.’”

01:03:22.431 --> 01:03:25.201 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Now, this is what’s going to happen.

01:03:25.201 --> 01:03:29.605 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And when you think about it,
this is just mind-boggling.

01:03:29.605 --> 01:03:31.974 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
They have no plans as such

01:03:31.974 --> 01:03:34.177 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
—the governments—
at this point.

01:03:35.711 --> 01:03:38.581 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So Jehovah forces

01:03:38.581 --> 01:03:41.150 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
one part of Satan’s system

01:03:41.150 --> 01:03:44.353 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to destroy another part.

01:03:44.353 --> 01:03:47.890 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Only the Almighty God can do that.

01:03:47.890 --> 01:03:52.161 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So when they do destroy Babylon the Great

01:03:52.161 --> 01:03:55.698 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and all of this is taking place on the earth,

01:03:55.698 --> 01:03:59.235 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
